Title: TARTE Tarteist Lip Paint 6 ml(SO FETCH)
Description: Paint on pigment to create a tarteist™ lip masterpiece with this chic, ultra-matte liquid lipstick. Designed for styles ranging from modern minimalist to bold and dramatic, this high-definition, saturated formula starts as a traditional lipstick that's been liquefied and concentrated, resulting in a luxurious, velvety texture with a sophisticated, matte finish. The full coverage formula comes in an array of on-trend bold and everyday shades and features a tarteist™ paint brush wand with an ergonomically slanted, soft applicator so anyone can paint on precise pigment no matter your tarteist™ skill level.

Title: L'Oreal Paris Color Riche Accords Intense 4.7 g(Sparkling Amethyst - 287)
Description: For that beach party, wear a little white dress and apply this Color Riche Lipstick from Loreal Paris to get that uniquely gorgeous look. Truly complementing your colorful nature, this Sparkling Amethyst - 287 shade from Loreal Paris gives you the look you always desired. The creamy texture of this Loreal Paris Lip Color perfectly glides on your lips and gives you an even application. Enriched with Vitamin E and Omega 3, this Loreal Paris Lip Color takes care of the sensitive skin of your lips. Vitamin E does not let your lips dry out unlike many other lipsticks that you would have applied earlier. Omega 3 keeps your lips moisturised and conditioned, making them softer and more supple. So this Loreal Paris Color Riche Accords Intense Lip Color offers you glamorous looking lips along with protecting them too. Directions for Use Dab a little foundation on your lips as a base. Gently apply this lipstick from the center of your upper lip and then towards the corner. Glide it on your lower lips as well and merge.

Title: Cartier Delices de Eau Fruitee EDT  -  100 ml
Description: A beautiful fragrance can make your day beautiful and bring out the best in you. The delightful Cartier Delices De Eau Fruitee is a delicate perfume that embraces your senses in a pleasantness. The sun-soaked freshness of this Gourmand Fruity Floral fragrance surrounds you in poetic fantasy and accentuates the gorgeous woman in you. Fruit of a perfumer’s stimulated imagination, this Cartier luxury Eau de Toilette embarks you on a soulful journey of irresistible fruity, sweet and spicy aromas in a charming, sophisticated vial that reminds you of the Morello Cherry that lies at the heart of this fragrance. The Cartier Delices De Eau Fruitee has sweet, warm notes of Morello Cherry and White Jasmine, Amber and Sambac Jasmine that create a natural, soothing impression. The lingering notes of this rich perfume also reflect the enchanting Amber, Sambac Jasmine, Orange Blossom, Pink Jasmine, White Peach, Vanilla and Tonka Bean. An amalgamation of pure and scintillating aromas, this sensual spray of fragrances evokes an ultimate sense of femininity and emotions that you simply fall in love with.

Title: TITAN SKINN VIALS MEN Eau de Parfum  -  8 ml(For Men)
Parfums Gres Cabotine EDT  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Youthful, fanciful, theatrical - the Cabotine woman pouts and flutters her flirty lids at you. Just a glance from her and the senses swoon, for just a smile men fall at her feet. Cabotine from Parfum Gres is more than just an essence - it's the aura of your essential femininity. Created by perfumer Jean-Claude Delville, Cabotine entices with its sensuality. Inspired by the exotic ginger lily that blooms only for a few days and wilts within hours, Cabotine is a metaphor for the transformation of an adolescent girl into a woman, and the fresh bloom of youthful sensuality. This Eau de Toilette features a top note of blackcurrant buds, plums, pears, and fresh coriander. The floral heart of rose, tuberose, ylang-ylang, ginger lily, hyacinth, freesia, violet and iris, trails into the intoxicating warmth of cedar wood, creamy vanilla, tonka beans, velvety musk and amber accords in the base note. Artistically crafted, Cabotine embodies the young at heart, the vibrant, the vivid and the utterly contemporary.

Description: Fragrances are created from essential oils present in plants, flowers, fruits, barks, roots, and animal secretions. And what precious pricey substances they are! In Grasse, France, the centre of the World Perfumery Industry, workers rise early to pick Jasmine before dawn. When the sun peeks over the horizon, the flower loses twenty percent of its aroma. A skilled harvester can pick about a pound of flowers in forty five minutes, or five thousand tiny blossoms. But only a few drops of essence will emerge after processing. Eight hundred pounds of Jasmine flowers, or four million flowers, yield just one pound of concentrated oil. And the price of the essences? One pound of this oil, called Jasmine Absolute will fetch from 80,000 to 1, 00,000, depending on quality, while Rose Absolute can cost as much as 2,50,000 to 3,00,000 per pound.
